ciscoNetintMIB.description: This MIB module is for Network Interrupt information on Cisco device.

cniThrottleTable.name: cniThrottleTable
cniThrottleTable.description: This table provides the network interrupt throttle counter information. An entry in this table is populated for each physical entity in the managed system capable of providing this information.

cniThrottleEntry.name: cniThrottleEntry
cniThrottleEntry.description: An entry containing information about network interrupt throttle counter.

cniThrottleCount.name: cniThrottleCount
cniThrottleCount.description: This object indicates the number of times network interrupt throttle has become active.

ciscoNetintMIBCompliance.name: ciscoNetintMIBCompliance
ciscoNetintMIBCompliance.description: The compliance statement for entities which implement the Cisco Netint MIB.

ciscoThrottleGroup.name: ciscoThrottleGroup
ciscoThrottleGroup.description: A collection of object providing network interrupt throttle count.
